</clause>
<clause id="_recommended_value_of_the_frequency_in_the_cipm_list_of_frequencies" obligation="normative"><title>Recommended value <eref type="inline" bibitemid="cctf21" citeas="[1]"/> of the frequency in the CIPM List of Frequencies</title><p id="_e3fc1fbd-d5b0-41c5-9abb-2b45392cd682">
