</math></stem>,</p>
<p id="_dfaf9a1f-9835-485f-aed2-c6efe56cc08c">with a relative standard uncertainty of <stem type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>1.5</mn><mo>&#215;</mo><msup><mrow><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow><mrow><mi>&#8722;</mi><mn>15</mn></mrow></mrow></msup></math></stem>.</p>
<p id="_6f013d05-5ad4-4c49-a3fb-f552a427af47">This radiation was endorsed by the CIPM as a secondary representation of the definition of the second <eref type="inline" bibitemid="ci2006" citeas="[2]"/>.</p></clause>
